- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper deals with the deployment of UAVs. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper discusses the optimization of energy usage in the UAV swarm. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes an algorithm for optimal deployment of UAVs. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the complexity and approximation algorithms for the deployment problem.
